# DDD Tactical Building Blocks & Review

Internal implementation of domain logic with a scoring rubric.

## ⭐ Scoring Rubric (0-10)
1. Immutability (Value Objects vs Primitives)
2. Invariants (Consistent Rules)
3. Encapsulation (Hidden Internals)
4. Identity (Stable Global Identity)
5. Ubiquity (Business Language)

## Tactical Elements
- Entity (identity)
- Value Object (immutable)
- Aggregate Root (consistency boundary)
- Domain Event (decoupled side-effects)
- Repository (storage interface)

## Workflows
1. Design Aggregates
2. Model Entities/VOs
3. Apply business rules in ARs
4. Collect/Publish Domain Events
